data.description: Welcome to this 1176 SF ranch nestled in a quiet neighborhood.   This beautiful and well-maintained Elida SD home is minutes from shopping and dining and is Move- in ready! This home offers 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathroom and a charming eat in kitchen, plenty of closet space and custom blinds and beautiful flooring throughout.  New roof in 2020.  Appliances includes washer, dryer, fridge and stove.
